---
title: Handoff Protocol v2 - State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE

    IDLE --> REQUESTING : agent.execute() called

    REQUESTING --> VALIDATING : Guardian G8 check PASS
    REQUESTING --> REQUESTING_FAILED : Guardian G8 check FAIL\nor no causal reason (G4)

    VALIDATING --> TRANSFERRING : confidence_level >= 0.60
    VALIDATING --> LOW_CONFIDENCE : confidence_level < 0.60

    LOW_CONFIDENCE --> TRANSFERRING : EVA-33 notified\noperator override OR\ndefault continue
    LOW_CONFIDENCE --> ESCALATED : operator HALT decision

    TRANSFERRING --> CONFIRMING : target agent ACK received
    TRANSFERRING --> TRANSFER_TIMEOUT : no ACK within 30s

    CONFIRMING --> COMPLETE : Genesis-MCP log written
    CONFIRMING --> TRANSFER_TIMEOUT : log write fails

    REQUESTING_FAILED --> REQUESTING : retry attempt 1 (delay 2s)
    TRANSFER_TIMEOUT --> TRANSFERRING : retry attempt 1-3\n(delay 2s, 4s, 8s)

    REQUESTING_FAILED --> ESCALATED : retry 3 exhausted
    TRANSFER_TIMEOUT --> ESCALATED : retry 3 exhausted

    ESCALATED --> [*] : ARB decision\n(retry_different_agent\nOR degrade_gracefully\nOR halt_chain)

    COMPLETE --> [*]

    note right of REQUESTING_FAILED
        Max retries: 3
        Backoff: 2s, 4s, 8s (cap 16s)
    end note

    note right of ESCALATED
        Genesis-MCP stores:\nevents.type = handoff_escalation\nwith trace_id
    end note
